        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1404202867" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6677288031010058979">This is a hard book for me to rate. I loved the characters, every one of them, even the ones I didn&apos;t agree with or disliked. I loved the action but sometimes it took too long to get to it. It is a long book, with a lot of info but I can&apos;t really see what could be dropped to shorten it, just sometimes, it was not exciting or quick moving.<br/><br/>Will read more by this author, but think I need some shorter, quicker, faster paced reads in between.</span>
  <span id="freeText6677288031010058979" style="display:none">This is a hard book for me to rate. I loved the characters, every one of them, even the ones I didn't agree with or disliked. I loved the action but sometimes it took too long to get to it. It is a long book, with a lot of info but I can't really see what could be dropped to shorten it, just sometimes, it was not exciting or quick moving.<br /><br />Will read more by this author, but think I need some shorter, quicker, faster paced reads in between.</span>
