      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/545.Neal_Stephenson">About Neal Stephenson</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/545.Neal_Stephenson"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1430920344p3/545.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/545.Neal_Stephenson">Neal Stephenson
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
23,316
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12941039811048960360">Neal Stephenson is the author of <i>Reamde, Anathem,</i> and the three-volume historical epic the Baroque Cycle (<i>Quicksilver, The Confusion,</i> and <i>The System of the World</i>), as well as <i>Cryptonomicon, The Diamond Age, Snow Crash,</i> and <i>Zodiac.</i> He lives in Seattle, Washington.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

